title: Guardians of the Galaxy - Annihilation
description:
I've been pulling together all the pre-MarvelNow material I could find on the Guardians of the Galaxy.

Most of the Annihilation storyline I could find, leading into the Annihilators, as well as the 25 issue Guardians run, seemed a good representation of their new origin.

Some digital files I couldn't find were the Realm and War of the Kings specials, but one can still follow the story.

Of note is the folder of supplementary material, including Groot's first appearance in the '60s Tales to Astonish.

If anyone has the complete digital files for Realm and War of the Kings, please remix and upload.
